wikipediaPreview: Fraser Anning's Conservative National Party is a far-right[1][2][3][4][5] political party in Australia[6][7] founded by Queensland senator Fraser Anning in April 2019. Anning was a senator for One Nation and Katter's Australian Party, and also sitting as an independent.
